## 4. Controller Form Errors Handler

### New regex + function

```python
FORM_ERRORS_RE = re.compile(r"\[\[FORM_ERRORS:(.*?)\]\]", re.DOTALL)

def _emit_with_form_errors(full_text: str):
    match = FORM_ERRORS_RE.search(full_text)
    if not match:
        yield {"type": "chunk", "text": full_text}
        return
    ...
    yield {"type": "form_errors", "form_id": payload.get("form_id"), "errors": payload.get("errors", {})}
    ...
```

### Marker detection ordering (both `stream_chat_with_orchestrator` and `stream_chat_with_file`)

```python
if "[[FORM_WIDGET:" in content:
    for event in _emit_with_form_widget(content): ...
elif "[[FORM_ERRORS:" in content:      # NEW
    for event in _emit_with_form_errors(content): ...
elif "<<FORM>>" in content and "<<ENDFORM>>" in content:
    # existing handler
else:
    yield {"type": "chunk", "text": content + "\n\n"}
